# 14 - Learning Plan Creator
# Generate personalized learning paths

NAME learning-planner
INPUT subject
INPUT current_level DEFAULT "beginner"
INPUT time_available DEFAULT "10 hours per week"
INPUT goal_timeline DEFAULT "3 months"

GOAL assess "Understand the learning scope: $subject at $current_level level, with $time_available available over $goal_timeline."
GOAL research "Research the best resources: books, courses, tutorials, and practice projects for $subject."
GOAL structure "Create a week-by-week learning plan with milestones, resources, and practice exercises."
GOAL output "Format as a clear, actionable plan with checkboxes for tracking progress. Save the plan to learning-plan-output.md."

RUN plan USING assess, research, structure, output
